targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  $__timeGroup(created, '5m', NULL) AS time,
  AVG(milliseconds) / 1000 AS OutboundICECollection
FROM
  UOWtimers
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created) AND (UOWType = 5)
  GROUP BY $__timeGroup(created, '5m', NULL)

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(created, '5m', NULL) AS time,
  AVG(milliseconds) / 1000 AS InboundICECollection
FROM
  UOWtimers
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created) AND (UOWType = 9)
  GROUP BY $__timeGroup(created, '5m', NULL)

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(created, '5m', NULL) AS time,
  AVG(milliseconds) / 1000 AS ConferenceICECollection
FROM
  UOWtimers
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created) AND (UOWType = 23)
  GROUP BY $__timeGroup(created, '5m', NULL)

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(created, '1h', NULL) AS time,
  COUNT(*) AS Successful
FROM
  subscriberLoginTransaction
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created) AND created IS NOT NULL
  AND failed = 0
  GROUP BY $__timeGroup(created, '1h', NULL)

SELECT
  $__timeGroup(created, '1h', NULL) AS time,
  COUNT(*) AS Failed
FROM
  subscriberLoginTransaction
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created) AND created IS NOT NULL
  AND failed = 1
  GROUP BY $__timeGroup(created, '1h', NULL)
